These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, jazz, techno
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | indie | dubstep   | techno | jazz    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, aquamarine, brown
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes grey is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who likes grey is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Color   | brown    | grey | aquamarine | emerald    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, trike, bus
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Transport   | trike        | bus     | car | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, photographer, nurse, librarian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the photographer is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the librarian is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | librarian | mechanic | photographer | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, handball, baseball, tennis
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | handball  | basketball    | baseball   | tennis       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

