.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, funk, folk, electronic
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, japanese, malaysian
1. the italian is in an even position##4
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the italian##1
3. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of soul##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | funk | electronic | soul |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian     | indonesian  | japanese  |

