.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, fanta, milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea   | 7up | fanta |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

