.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, nurse, scientist, electrician
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the electrician##1
2. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the electrician is between the mechanic and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the electrician is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the nurse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Job   | scientist | nurse | electrician        | mechanic    |

