.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, red, fuchsia, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, light-blue-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is light-blue-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is light-blue-polo is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | brown   | light-blue   | red      | fuchsia      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | light-blue-polo | biathlon |

