.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, camping, baking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, hip-hop, soul
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of disco and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | baking | chess  | camping  | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | hip-hop | ambient | disco   |

