.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, september, february
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Birthday           | february     | march     | september   | april         |

