.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, drama, adventure, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching drama movies##2
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | drama         | mystery   | adventure |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

