3. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | r&b | house    | indie |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

