.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, lemonade, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person drinking water is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage         | coffee   | lemonade | milk | water    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

