.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, tulip, aconite
1. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
7. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Flower       | orchid  | tulip | aconite | dahlia  |

