.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
House: victorian, cottage, ranch-style, colonial
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
3. the cottage house is between the entrepreneur and the victorian house##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| House   | colonial          | cottage | victorian         | ranch-style  |

 